# --- .NET Core / .NET 5+ Recursive Ignores ---
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/[Pp]ublish/

# --- IDE & OS Specific (Recursive) ---
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.ide/
**/*.user
**/*.userosscache
**/*.suo
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Project Settings (Recursive) ---
# Ignores local launch settings (ports/env vars) for all projects
**/[Pp]roperties/launchSettings.json

# --- Secrets & Config ---
# NEVER commit these to GitHub
**/[Aa]ppsettings.json
**/[Aa]ppsettings.Production.json
**/[Aa]ppsettings.Development.json
**/[Aa]ppsettings.Local.json
**/.env
**/*.pfx
**/*.publishsettings

# --- Logs ---
*.log
**/logs/
**/[Vv]log/

# --- Package Manager ---
**/[Pp]ackages/
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
